program in Native American

00:01:03.530 --> 00:01:06.550
and Indigenous Studies.

00:01:06.550 --> 00:01:07.320
But moving on.

00:01:07.320 --> 00:01:07.820
Back to Rob.

00:01:07.820 --> 00:01:10.060
