00:01:20.280 --> 00:01:23.480
His work at Syracuse,
where he founded a research

00:01:23.480 --> 00:01:26.440
based law and policy
institute that

00:01:26.440 --> 00:01:30.370
focuses on indigenous nations
and their interactions

00:01:30.370 --> 00:01:32.720
