00:06:31.430 --> 00:06:34.930
A little story about when
I was running for office

00:06:34.930 --> 00:06:39.170
in 2010 as the candidate for
President of the Seneca Nation.

00:06:39.170 --> 00:06:42.890
A couple of our elders
were very, very worried

00:06:42.890 --> 00:06:44.290
and concerned about me.

00:06:47.430 --> 00:06:51.650
You're licensed by the state
